  "text": "For the T-shape adaptation task, the method was as in [CITATION_1] . This task matched the eye-height adaptation task in method, except that the adaptors and test stimuli were T-shapes, matched in size to the T-shaped eyes-nose-mouth region of the faces in the face-height task (Fig. 2c ).",
